  <context>
    <background>
      `FinancialCalculatorHandler` performs deterministic financial computations on
      structured numeric input — typically extracted line items from an invoice or
      contract by an upstream `EntityExtractorHandler` or `InvoiceExtractionToolHandler`.
      Because the math is pure, the handler is fast, testable, and audit-friendly
      (auditors can replay calculations on identical inputs and get identical outputs).

      The handler is distinct from `FinancialCalculationToolHandler` (task 104) which
      handles formula-driven calculations (rate × principal × time). This handler is
      for aggregation + tax/discount/FX math on already-extracted figures.
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Handlers/FinancialCalculatorHandler.cs (NEW)</file>
